title: 10/24: Mid-season Awards; Trade Talk; Regulators; MIA-HOU (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Today's show is sponsored by PUBG Mobile. Download the game in your app store, then go to www.pubgmobile.com/redeem/global, insert your character ID and this promo code to win a reward: HOVZBZ9PE
Let's start with some emails as we answer your questions about Courtland Sutton, the JAC DST, Tre'Quan Smith and more. Then we've got Buy Low (8:22) and Sell High (10:10) players for you to consider ... Rest of season rankings (18:34) as we discuss Cook vs. Fournette vs. Ingram, Coleman vs. Chubb vs. Peterson and Allen vs. Golladay vs. Landry. Then we've got our Mid-season Awards including MVP and Busts (21:25), Fantasy Regulators Part One (36:00) and a MIA-HOU preview (38:25) ... Answering a bunch of tweets about a bunch of players (46:42), Grade the Trade (52:41) and more Fantasy Regulators (54:45) to end the show ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
